Author: back2decembr
Text: Coffee dates are always a safe option for me if I want to be social but not feel pressure to consume calories. I just claim to be swamped with work/meetings during the lunchtime hour and ask if they can do mid-afternoon coffee instead. Works everytime

Author: kb3rry
Text: Go on a thrifting date instead. I could spend the whole day browsing and not think about food.
